parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft position sensor can cause the engine to stall, leading to a potential crash without warning.
The failure of spark plugs can cause engine damage, cylinder damage, and potentially lead to engine failure, resulting in costly repairs and potentially causing accidents.
Engine failure can cause sudden loss of power, stalling, and potentially lead to accidents, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
Fuel system failure can cause strong odors of fuel fumes, potentially leading to explosions or fires.
The cruise control defect can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential fires.
symptoms: The cruise control becomes stuck in the on position
causing the vehicle to accelerate rapidly

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the accelerator cable can cause the vehicle to stall, lose control, and lead to accidents.
symptoms: and the vehicle speed increases unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Warped front rotors can cause uneven braking, leading to reduced stopping power, increased stopping distances, and potentially, accidents.
Total brake failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially, injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature wear of front disc brake pads can cause reduced braking performance, increased stopping distances, and potentially, accidents.
symptoms: Squealing or grinding noises when braking

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS system failure can cause loss of traction, skidding, and accidents, especially on slippery or uneven road surfaces.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Warped Rotors and Brake Pad Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The warped rotors and worn-out brake pads can cause the vehicle to shudder or vibrate when braking, leading to loss of control and increased stopping distance, which can result in accidents.
The interference between the wheel and torsion bar can cause the vehicle to lose control, especially during sharp turns, which can lead to accidents.
